metadata.name: Respect Our Artists
metadata.description:
As we build our new digital art renaissance it is important to respect the way display the new art.
This was a picture I took and became a meme. 
It shows how NOT to display art work. 
I decided to mint it. So, I can take ownership over my on me and seize the meme back for provenance.
All proceeds will got to buying more art and displaying it all at multiple events correctly.
